(ooc: hotmail never delivered my post, so I'll send another one. I'm in a 
big hurry right now, but my last post was with Mantle and the eletors 
forming Element and charging at Abominus and firing)

Element slowed down, looking ahead at Abominus. He was running slightly 
slower, but he was still running. He carefully guided the missiles he had 
fired at Abominus's head, and then brought up a rifle and fired two shots 
from it. His spark was beating fast with excitement. He loved battle.


Cyndro saw that his attacks were coming close to hitting friends, so he 
concentrated alot of his fire on the gestalts instead. Two missile launchers 
aimed at each one, firing two missiles each at every enemy gestalt on the 
field. The other defences all focused on the new enemies (KSLawdoggie's 
troops :). EMP cannons, autogunfire, and an occasional missile shot out at 
each one. The jammer device was still fully funtional, and the Element's 
shields blazed with full power. The Maximals wouldn't lose this one.
